      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ARCHITECTURE SUMMARY\n\nTotal Architecture: ~12,000+ lines of code across 50+ core files\nFrontend: ~7,900 LOC (ThreadComponent, streaming, hooks, stores, tool views)\nShared Package: ~3,800 LOC (types, streaming core, tool utilities, animations)\nBackend Services: ~1,100 LOC (kortix-router, kortix-auth, kortix-cloud)\nSandbox: Docker container with OpenCode framework, 8 agents, 22 skills, 8 tools, background services",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 132,
      "containerId": "summary-box",
      "originalText": "ARCHITECTURE SUMMARY\n\nTotal Architecture: ~12,000+ lines of code across 50+ core files\nFrontend: ~7,900 LOC (ThreadComponent, streaming, hooks, stores, tool views)\nShared Package: ~3,800 LOC (types, streaming core, tool utilities, animations)\nBackend Services: ~1,100 LOC (kortix-router, kortix-auth, kortix-cloud)\nSandbox: Docker container with OpenCode framework, 8 agents, 22 skills, 8 tools, background services",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
